text: Dominic Wynn Woods (born June 20, 1992), better known by his stage name Sage the Gemini, is an American rapper, singer, songwriter and record producer. He is from Fairfield, California. He is a member of The HBK Gang. He is known for his single "Gas Pedal", featuring Iamsu!, which peaked at #29 on the Billboard Hot 100.http://www.billboard.com/artist/2549565/sage-the-gemini/chart Sage The Gemini – Chart history This made it both artists' first top-40 hit.
